{"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme\/init(fontFamily:tuning:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangebusinesstools\/orangebusinesstoolstheme"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools"]]},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"final"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Usages","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Usages"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Some products may have heavy and very rich user interfaces with a lot of components and elements to displays and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with which users can interact. Thus for such products there are specific constraints of spaces and sizes, even if","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these products must be Orange flavored.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"That is the reason why this team is created: a kind of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeTheme"},{"text":" but wih adjustments on some tokens like spacings and sizings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To get the theme:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Integration","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Integration"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To use this theme, inject it to your view using ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"text":" and get it through environment variable.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @main","    struct YourApp: App {","        var body: some Scene {","            WindowGroup {","                OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeBusinessToolsTheme()) {","                    \/\/ Your root view","                }","            }","        }","    }"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Theme-tuning","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Theme tuning"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be customized a bit for more flexibility thanks to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Tuning"},{"type":"text","text":" object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You just need to give a predefined tuning configuration at theme init to build the one you need."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To apply the tuning:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your theme tuning","    let tuning = Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true)","","    \/\/ Apply it to your theme","    let theme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: tuning)","    \/\/ Or in one line","    let theme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true))","","    \/\/ Or apply predefined tunings","    let orangeFranceTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeFrance)","    let orangeBusinessTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeBusiness)","    let maxitTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(tuning: Tuning.MaxIt)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Typography","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Typography"},{"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Helvetica Neue"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange brand strongly relies on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family. Thus each Orange brand should, or must, use it."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family is available at system level, so it is not needed to get it through external assets."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"By default an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" uses as font family the token "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault"},{"type":"text","text":", which is today "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Helvetica Neue"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use another font family, you will have to send the suitable token or the suitable font family."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, beware, iOS API relies also on the PostScript name of the font."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To be sure of the value to use, look at the font book of your device."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is recommended to use the font raw tokens."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ The following instanciations work","    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme()","    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(fontFamily: OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault)","    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(fontFamily: \"HelveticaNeue\") \/\/ Which is PostScript name of the font","    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue\")"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue-Arabic","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family does not manage arabic alphabet but latin one, it is possible apply another font family to the theme like the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":". This font family assets can be retrieved through the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"PostScript name management has been implemented for this font family, thus the weight are managed and it is only needed to add the font assets to the project,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"register them and define the font family name to use.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    let orangeTheme = OrangeBusinessToolsTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue Arabic\")"],"type":"codeListing"},{"name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.17.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The `Orange Business Tools`` theme is an Orange theme but tailored for some products with heavy UI.","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"],"type":"inheritsFrom"},{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/SQ","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","symbolKind":"class","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:29OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools0bcD5ThemeC","roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange Business Tools"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","kind":"identifier"}]},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools":{"type":"topic","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orangebusinesstools.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangebusinesstools","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange Business Tools theme is dedicated to applications with strong dimensions constraints."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools","role":"collection","title":"Theme Orange Business Tools"},"ic_theme_orangebusinesstools.png":{"identifier":"ic_theme_orangebusinesstools.png","type":"image","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/ic_theme_orangebusinesstools.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/OUDSTheme":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/oudstheme","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a basic theme any theme must be a subclass off, or all themes must have as ancestor."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A Swift "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"class"},{"type":"text","text":" has been used so as to allow to easily override some attributes and have inheritance, without having for developers"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to implement all tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any properties of an overridable theme should be defined so as to provide defaults values."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"We allow this theme to be derivated and be overriden."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" can be seen as a kind of “abstract class” in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"object oriented paradigm"}]},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme contract"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" is not a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"final"}]},{"type":"text","text":" class, its type cannot be seen as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Sendable"},{"type":"text","text":", that is the reason why this conformity is unchecked."}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSTheme"},"https://brand.orange.com/en/brand-basics/typography":{"identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","title":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)","type":"link","url":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Brand website (authentication needed)"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/SQ":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/SQ","title":"Swift.Equatable","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangebusinesstools\/orangebusinesstoolstheme","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The `Orange Business Tools`` theme is an Orange theme but tailored for some products with heavy UI."}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme","role":"symbol","title":"OrangeBusinessToolsTheme"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/documentation/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme/init(fontFamily:tuning:)":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorangebusinesstools\/orangebusinesstoolstheme\/init(fontfamily:tuning:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Constructor of the OrangeBusinessTools theme with its own providers of tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It uses also the providers of charts colors from Orange theme ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeThemeColorChartSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"fontFamily","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic010FontFamilyB5Tokena","text":"FontFamilySemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tuning","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract6Tuninga","text":"Tuning","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/OrangeBusinessToolsTheme\/init(fontFamily:tuning:)","role":"symbol","title":"init(fontFamily:tuning:)"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrangeBusinessTools\/s16SendableMetatypeP","title":"Swift.SendableMetatype","type":"unresolvable"}}}